Description:
In a corner you find a rat man looking through some crates, when he sees you, he says:

"Hu... ho... don't hurt me! I'm alive! I'm alive! Or at least for the moment... 

I had to take a chance and get out of the palisade... we've run out of food and we're not going to last long. But there's nothing left here, I only found an old mysterious key and little else.
DescriptionAction: Won't you have some food for me?"
